      "message": "Patch Set 7:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/0f44650c-67a8-11e3-94a5-52540035b04c).  Ran 23 tests.  2 tests failed: conf-sanity, sanity.",
